      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine is currently running rough with a noticeable knock, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Visually, the car has substantial rust along the rocker panels, a cracked windshield, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn. It is best suited for a mechanic looking for a project or for someone needing a parts donor vehicle.",
