    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to a standard that defies its previous ownership. This motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a pristine exterior and a cabin that remains in showroom condition. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its original factory specifications. For the discerning individual who demands nothing less than perfection, this acquisition offers an unparalleled investment in automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
